precis:
Regulations Amending the APPLICATION OF PROVINCIAL LAWS REGULATIONS which
will enable law enforcement authorities in Manitoba, New Brunswick,
Newfoundland, Nova Scotia and Prince Edward Island to prosecute and process
federal contraventions committed in their territorial jurisdiction using
their own respective offence procedures.
